        <updateDate>2018-10-09T16:13:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Human Trafficking Survivor Tax Relief Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income civil damages, restitution, or other monetary awards (including compensatory or statutory damages and restitution imposed in a criminal matter) awarded to victims of peonage, slavery, or human trafficking. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
